<PageLayout title="About DJ Misha" description="Learn about DJ Misha, a professional San Diego DJ with over 15 years of experience specializing in weddings, corporate events, and private parties.">

  <p>DJ Misha is a professional San Diego DJ specializing in weddings, corporate events, private parties, and nightlife entertainment. With over 15 years of experience in the industry, DJ Misha brings passion, expertise, and the perfect mix of music to every event.</p>

  <h2>The DJ Misha Story</h2>
  <p>DJ Misha started DJ'ing in 2001, the year he fell in love with dance music and wanted to give people the same feeling he had experienced when listening and dancing to an amazing DJ set.</p>

  <p>DJ technology has evolved dramatically in the last decade, but the essence of the DJ has remained the same. The job is simple: select good music and blend it to create an experience.</p>

  <h2>Top Rated DJ Services</h2>
  <p>DJ Misha is rated 5/5 stars based on 83 reviews. Our clients consistently praise the energy, music selection, and professionalism that DJ Misha brings to every event.</p>

  <h2>Music Genres and Styles</h2>
  <p>Playing House Music, EDM, Electronic Dance Music, Deep House, Techno, Electronica, Nu Disco, Downtempo, Lounge, Progressive, Electro, Trance, Underground, Pop, Future Hits and much more...</p>

